        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks GR for his notes and essays [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">10581</hi>].</p>  
<p>Similar appendages to those GR mentions [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">10581</hi>] appear on the necks of goats, but the idea of reversion to a common progenitor of goats and pigs "stumps" CD.</p> 
